<p>A REMARKABLE swordsman</p>
<section class = "timeline">
<ul>
<li>1842 or 1844 - Born in Shirakawa Domain's Edo mansion
<li>1851 or 1853- At the age of nine, Okita starts training with Kondo Shusuke (third master of the Tennen Rishin-ryū)
<li>1860 or 1862 - Around the age of 18, mastered all the techniques of the Tennen Rishin-ryu school
<li>1863 - Shinsengumi founded to protect Shogunate representatives in Kyoto
<li>1863 - Okita Sōji becomes vice-commander's assistant of the Shinsengumi
<li>1865 - Becomes captain of the first unit of the Shinsengumi
<li>1868 - death during the Boshin war
</section>
<div>
<p class = "quote">"Don't worry. You won't get hurt if you don't get hit."</p>
